snippet.title: Exiles Release Trailer for Android
snippet.description:
Download Exiles here on Google Play:
https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.crescentmoongames.exiles

Exiles is an epic sci fi RPG for Android devices.
The follow up to the fantastic open world game, Ravensword: Shadowlands by Crescent Moon Games. Coming December 18th to Android!
